Yes — these screenshots are enough. I would not make a bunch of new random changes. The proper final fix is mainly to clean up the preserve decision so the role has one clear variable that means:

“This path exists and is protected, so do not back it up and do not copy over it.”

Right now your copy_managed_path.yml is close, but I would still refine it so it is less confusing and easier to verify.

1. backup_item.yml

Leave this file alone.

It is not responsible for deciding whether something should be backed up. It only backs up when another task includes it.

